high_descs: move left to the sink
pick up a knife from the sink
turn around to the table
slice the potato on the table
turn left to the fridge
place the knife in the fridge
turn around and head to the table
pick up a potato slice from the table
turn left and head to the fridge
place the slice to cool in the fridge and then take it out
turn right to the table
place the cooked slice on the table
anns.task_desc: place a cooked potato slice on the table

high_descs: Turn and go to the sink.
Pick up the knife that is on the counter in front of the sink.
With the knife in hand turn and go to the island counter on the side where the stove is to the potato on the counter.
With the knife slice half  the potato starting from your left side.
With the knife in hand turn and go to the fridge.
Open fridge and place knife on the top shelf front and center.
Go to the island counter on the side where the stove is to the potato on the counter.
Pick up the middle slice of potato.
With the potato in hand turn and go to the fridge.
Open fridge. Place potato to the left of the knife.  Close fridge. Open fridge and grab potato slice on the top shelf. Close fridge.
With the potato slice in hand turn and go to the counter to the left of the sink.
Place the potato in front of the toaster slightly to the right.
anns.task_desc: Slice potato, put in fridge and on counter.

high_descs: Walk around the kitchen island to reach the sink.
Pick up the large knife from the sink.
Make a left to walk back to the kitchen island where the potato is.
Slice the potato with the large knife on the counter.
Turn left to walk to the fridge.
Set the knife down in the fridge.
Turn right and make a left around the kitchen island to the potato.
Pick up a slice of potato.
Turn left and walk back to the fridge.
Chill the potato slice in the fridge, removing it afterwards.
Turn around and walk to the toaster.
Set the potato slice on the counter in front of the toaster.
anns.task_desc: Chill a potato slice in the fridge to put on the counter.
